Package: regdatasets
Title: Datasets for Teaching Regression Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("JoonHo", "Lee", , "jlee296@ua.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-4019-8703"))
Description: A curated collection of datasets for teaching introductory
    and intermediate regression analysis in education and social science
    contexts. Includes datasets for simple and multiple linear regression,
    ANOVA/ANCOVA, logistic regression, and ordinal response models.
    Datasets are sourced from published textbooks and research studies,
    covering topics such as student achievement (GCSE, PISA, NAEP),
    crime rates, faculty salaries, and survey data.
